      Reena Shrestha
      October 10
      checkmarkcaution-solid

      Life is not run by any formulae, not by any theories, neither by any rule. Its just collection of random event, random number, random luck, random unluck and random errors I think it is governed by nothing. There is no guarantee of your good outcome with hard work and neither bad outcomes with bad deeds. Something can just happen without reason.
      I thought life is intelligent but its just a mere randomness.
      When adversity strikes in our life, there are only two options left .. Accept what Is or Suffer. I think both are awful.
